<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>و <span class="c4">[غَزاة]</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span> بني قُرَيظة <span class="c2">(٢)</span>، وغَزاة الخندق <span class="c2">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[السادسة]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>غَزاة عُسْفان <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>ووفد السباع <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وغَزوة الحُدَيبْية <span class="c2">(٦)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وبَيعة الرضوان <span class="c2">(٧)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>* * *<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وبعث الرسول إلى يَزْدَجرد <span class="c2">(٨)</span>، وقيصر <span class="c2">(٩)</span>. ولما وصل كتابه إلى ملك الفُرس<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>مزَّقَه،<span class="c5"> فدعا عليه رسول الله <span class="special">ﷺ</span> فقال:</span> <span class="c1">"مزق الله مُلْكه"</span> فكان ذلك <span class="c2">(١٠)</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[السابعة]</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>غَزاة خَيبر <span class="c2">(١١)</span>.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">وكتب رسول الله <span class="special">ﷺ</span>:</span> <span class="c1">"بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمَنِ الرَّحِيمِ"</span> <span class="c2">(١٢)</span>.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">واتخذ خاتمًا ونقشه:</span> <span class="c1">"محمَّد رسول الله"</span>.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
